<quantity box="[1105,1217,1564,1590]" metricMagnitude="-4" metricUnit="m" metricValue="1.5" pageId="25" pageNumber="26" unit="mm" value="0.15">0.15 mm</quantity>
, slightly curved ventrally; clasper length 
